&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/USA-DALLAS-MANSION-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4327&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/USA-DALLAS-MANSION-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;USA- DALLAS- MANSION- OFFER- LOGO1&quot; width=&quot;184&quot; height=&quot;64&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.gayot.com/restaurants/mansion-restaurant-rosewood-mansion-turtle-creek-dallas-tx-75219_15df99101-01.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-5441&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-GAYOT-LOGO-SMALL.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- GAYOT LOGO SMALL&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;64&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Dallas has earned a spot on the culinary map thanks in large part to Mansion Restaurant Chef Bruno Davaillon, who puts a French touch to Texas ingredients. The dining room&rsquo;s historic character blends beautifully with contemporary design. Mansion Restaurant earned a place on the &lt;strong&gt;2014 Gayot Top 40 Restaurants &lt;/strong&gt;in the U.S. list. Business casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Book your reservation &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.opentable.com/the-mansion-restaurant-at-rosewood-mansion-on-turtle-creek-reservations-dallas?rid=5135&amp;amp;restref=5135&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;online&nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;or contact the restaurant by phone at +1-214-443-4747 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:mansion.restaurant@rosewoodhotels.com&quot;&gt;mansion.restaurant@rosewoodhotels.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please provide a cell phone number or local (hotel) contact number in Dallas. The restaurant will call you the day prior to the dining date to reconfirm and discuss any allergies or special needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

